Revision history for Template::Flute::Style::CSS

0.0025 Sun Jan 29 15:15:22 2012 CET

    [BUGFIX]

    * Fix bug disregarding zero margin.

    [ENHANCEMENTS]

    * Acknowledge translate function in transform property.
    * Extend regular expression on transform property to allow real
      numbers and negative angles for rotate value. 

0.0024 Sun Jan 22 14:32:59 2012 CET

    [ENHANCEMENTS]

    * Add support for display property.
    * Add support for text-decoration property
    * Add support for the various transform CSS properties.

    [BUG FIXES]

    * Fix CSS specificity of tag selectors.
    * Fix bug determining border properties triggered by second class
      overriding specific border property.

0.0003  Wed May 25 11:03:06 2011 CEST
	
    [BUG FIXES]

    * Fix properties for tag.class selectors.

0.0002  Wed Apr 13 18:31:37 2011 CEST

    [ENHANCEMENTS]

    * Add support for list-style CSS property.
    * Add support for external stylesheets on local file system.
    * Add test for loading example stylesheet.

    [BUG FIXES]

    * Fix MANIFEST.

0.0001  Sun Mar 13 15:40:50 2011 CET

    * Initial release.
